---
---
<section class="want" id="want">
  <div class="wrap want-inner">
    <h2 class="reveal">The right people should already know your name.</h2>
    <p class="support reveal d1">
      You're good at what you do. Growing who knows it comes down to one thing: showing up
      where they are, week after week. The name you build is yours. It travels, whatever changes at work.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cost-section" style="padding-top:0">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 class="reveal">Being seen shouldn't cost you your time or your budget.</h2>
    <div class="cost-grid">
      <div class="cost-card card reveal d1">
        <div class="cost-who">Doing it yourself</div>
        <div class="cost-big">10 hours</div>
        <div class="cost-unit">a week you don't have</div>
      </div>
      <div class="vs-badge reveal d2">vs</div>
      <div class="cost-card card reveal d3">
        <div class="cost-who">Hiring an agency</div>
        <div class="cost-big">$3,000–$25,000</div>
        <div class="cost-unit">a month, with a stranger in charge of your voice</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="better-way reveal d4">There's a better way. ↓</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.want { text-align: center; }
.want .support { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

.cost-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
  gap: 0 20px;
  align-items: center;
  margin-top: 36px;
  max-width: 680px;
}
.cost-card { padding: 32px 28px; }
.cost-who {
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--faint);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.cost-big {
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 5vw, 2.2rem);
  letter-spacing: -.025em;
  line-height: 1.05;
  color: var(--ink);
}
.cost-unit { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 8px; }
.vs-badge {
  width: 44px; height: 44px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--bg-2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--faint);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.better-way {
  margin-top: 28px;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.3rem);
  color: var(--gold-dk);
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .cost-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; }
  .vs-badge { margin: 0 auto; }
}
</style>
